","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"1","text":"4. Por perfil molecular (en\\Nadenocarcinoma) (4)","guid":"yA1rjzfnaH-hwLmpYBkfEA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"- Mutaciones activadoras de EGFR","guid":"Xc3MaQTrHR1kQ2M-YdfsDg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"- Reordenamientos de ALK","guid":"f5E1kiSEe-bdACNUv451Pg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"- Reordenamientos de ROS1","guid":"hw2XEvI4Px0o3jnEbcsSgQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"- Mutaciones de BRAF V600E","guid":"cUT8A3SAcRM4i2OjcXD7Yg","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"- Mutaciones de KRAS","guid":"ADZyPLSKXbbGP8Qx3e9ONA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"33","text":"- Otras alteraciones moleculares","guid":"61Jcn1KCYkp3Qnc6zypysw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación general de paciente\\Ncon cáncer de pulmón","guid":"E5i79t-BW29LiuVWQokmYg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"1. Historia clínica (1)","guid":"aonWRUec2bVR0REnhriisA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"- Síntomas\\Nrespiratorios","guid":"-s-6ssKUPAWDTyBMdQx7wg","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"- Tos","guid":"Tve41gAOlTI6BZcdBnl6yg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"- Disnea","guid":"5Mhp0Xf83YRn0uaLTa2sgg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"- Hemoptisis","guid":"sQc818bRpQDMAww3ybrMVA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"- Dolor torácico","guid":"ZbP3S98TCrpUzegEq-QshQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"- Síntomas\\Nsistémicos","guid":"3g1OcQ_2O4NHIabs_w5p8g","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"- Pérdida de peso","guid":"Nr2WBczunWeT-MNCdKzqyA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"- Astenia","guid":"_IjZ3e9Mw8vm09JdIdrvQg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"- Anorexia","guid":"GDmunzTEzu8grvpJKKe-ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"41","text":"- Historia de\\Ntabaquismo","guid":"x3AGb15YjD9b8OW4Z3QXCg","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"- Historia de\\Ntabaquismo (1)","guid":"oBym320JdTVSZJoJjbsBKQ","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- Edad de inicio","guid":"o_ACIgUfN3YDZluaMIHtXw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"- Cantidad de cigarrillos/día","guid":"LN57ftXD8zYMxK23uXbFaA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"- Años de consumo","guid":"AWq-DCsm2l24hMZn9gS4Ng","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"51","text":"- Paquetes-año (PA) = (cigarrillos/día\\N÷ 20) × años de consumo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"→ PA ≥ 30 → Alto riesgo de cáncer de pulmón (2)","guid":"NIm9w5miPGdnGvJVnDS2zA","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"51","text":"- Tipo de\\Ntabaco","guid":"m3aAMq7vJyh_riNlUEeRZg","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- Cigarrillos","guid":"OQK2h9er_X4bHjZo46xuMg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"- Puros","guid":"I7jf9s_h7mJaxE3D6s0WNg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"- Pipa","guid":"pVAjJY_DbW1-7mQEzxnO-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"51","text":"- Exposición a humo (3)","guid":"_XlSeqdrMNVap66EuBkA_Q","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"51","text":"Índice paquete-año\\N(IPA) (1)","guid":"AsljwI-H5x0jhswiwv9kGA","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"1. Definición","guid":"INoMfFgmH4zXuMgltClv4A","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Medida cuantitativa de la exposición acumulada al tabaco a lo largo de la vida (2)","guid":"2ctQ_rCcjawqInvdDQWZhA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"- Integra la cantidad y la duración del consumo de cigarrillos","guid":"wKnG_KMyrXfI3BTkcNmq8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"63","text":"2. Fórmula (3)","guid":"XTS2bBXFB5G1nIdztqi8pQ","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"IPA = (cigarrillos/día ÷ 20) × años de consumo","guid":"sJJKSjv2H538HG7Tgxr3gw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"- 20 cigarrillos = 1 paquete","guid":"WWUV1pvYogV97pPVhpafMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"63","text":"3. Interpretación (4)","guid":"OqF5x6BVoOb7D8L8pSLUIA","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- IPA < 10 → Bajo riesgo de enfermedades relacionadas con el tabaco","guid":"G1Js5NInOJKsq5KTWY95Vw","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"- IPA 10-20 → Riesgo moderado","guid":"BjWuTQ3Hp7D-IA40udUnbA","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"- IPA > 20 → Alto riesgo","guid":"hdLjDtpCo57pFzX6lz1kvg","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"→ Riesgo de cáncer de pulmón ↑ 60-70 veces en comparación con no fumadores (5)","guid":"P7DFo8dBUTh3Y2EMnBUqrg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"63","text":"4. Utilidad clínica","guid":"ZRdXm2cFvRcsKBVYJd9BDw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- Evaluación del\\Nriesgo de (6)","guid":"yfaJ4GZc5as3DTS-Sdu3hw","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"- Cáncer de pulmón","guid":"9AEl_Nz7lTjDB_zK33GIGg","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"- EPOC","guid":"aSfkJl9AYdAVswi0DLFJKQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"- Enfermedad cardiovascular","guid":"G-bW-qOvQsqk-MTJF-aJZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"- Selección de pacientes para screening de cáncer de pulmón (7)","guid":"Z-1OmTnWOTZ7M01GYx481w","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"- Edad 55-74 años + IPA ≥ 30 → TC de baja dosis anual","guid":"Lk-adt7_aDASmbnk58eTPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"75","text":"- Priorización de intervenciones para cesación tabáquica (8)","guid":"-53e8F7YT69OcMio6OBstQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"→ IPA elevado → Mayor beneficio de dejar de fumar","guid":"R5Trsn1geT_Eyu5vIgsKug","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"63","text":"5. Limitaciones (9)","guid":"HlU3bmwk4zBENO7N1KIeRg","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"- No considera","guid":"zPHDetlHzWDQgWBZms88tg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Tipo de tabaco (cigarrillos, puros, pipa)","guid":"am7ffac_zXpGXXJnjnontw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Patrón de inhalación","guid":"ImwVAC9ay-kmFYyU4NfwxQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Exposición al humo de segunda mano","guid":"lnqV2ETtPKwQF75rJtUSDw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"- Uso de productos de tabaco sin humo","guid":"vTiWouTE707p8iExwn60wQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"84","text":"- Puede subestimar el riesgo en fumadores de larga data con bajo consumo diario","guid":"uwkdk5MBUeTcquarMHZ5HQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"41","text":"- Exposición a otros carcinógenos (asbesto, radón)","guid":"-9s7pz0mPVisD7Rp6c1PAg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"41","text":"- Antecedentes familiares de cáncer de pulmón","guid":"cAVfKvttOAAnG9oQ0kC2YQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"40","text":"2. Examen\\Nfísico (2)","guid":"kbjB1-bHg5Sk6XeDG04dJQ","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"- Signos de\\Nobstrucción bronquial","guid":"CJNJOAo_ZuIqq29_6oZbww","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"- Sibilancias","guid":"CS9FYsfPuYDGAs204OPFKg","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"- Estridor","guid":"_v25U75_EhT4R-2RK_qopg","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"- Signos de\\Nextensión local","guid":"Lw-80GJHjxXnC68R8HRr2g","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Síndrome de Horner","guid":"JnQRrCRsD0UCDYxCU7KnUA","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Tríada clínica: miosis + ptosis + anhidrosis facial ipsilateral (1)","guid":"Fr1gHHzZxUIn8GLuQmR5xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Interrupción de vía simpática a ojo y cara (2)","guid":"2Ir1M1BTK041LjyRjQoS6w","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Lesión en neuronas de 1er, 2do o 3er orden (3)","guid":"EA6Excve-hejlSlRpKi5Ww","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"98","text":"Etiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Central (1er orden)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"ACV, tumor, desmielinización, siringomielia (4)","guid":"TpQcYPKuMwds8gmS5gZi0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"Preganglionar\\N(2do orden)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Tu. vértice pulmonar (Pancoast) (5)","guid":"2NJLZfx8xxmaIbWtdL6uLQ","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Cirugía de cuello, disección carotídea (6)","guid":"ylkWDkSi9pJ4Y6F06cGPUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"104","text":"Postganglionar (3er orden)","guid":"MpU7d00YtnDEl7cAr5moTg","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Cefalea en racimos, migraña, sd. carótida cavernosa (7)","guid":"36IOmvOhGfIQaySVbBF8-g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"98","text":"Clínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Miosis (pupila pequeña)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"Ptosis leve (caída párpado superior)","guid":"23ie4wD0D2MKG5fM9bwLGg","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Anhidrosis facial ipsilateral (disminución sudoración)","guid":"NaurDDuIIQ6dgZtoMHgOTg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Enoftalmos aparente (hundimiento ocular)","guid":"KYRZ6iG47ZlFFiKB5Z_Y4A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"97","text":"- Síndrome de vena\\Ncava superior","guid":"Y7LnFzPr6jp4zR-WSzOlcQ","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Perlas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"- ¿Cuál es la causa más frecuente de SVCS? Cáncer de pulmón, responsable de hasta el 80% de los casos. (1)","guid":"ITIRkEHkQTxuBAEz3DUDOQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"- ¿Qué hallazgo radiológico es característico del SVCS? Disminución del calibre de la vena cava superior. (2)","guid":"1GQphclUqxzRIfhUL1INBw","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"- ¿Cuál es el tratamiento de primera línea para el SVCS? Radioterapia y quimioterapia, dependiendo de la etiología subyacente. (3)","guid":"y_w6yGYzR8DsFLydtsItkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"117","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"- El SVCS es un conjunto de signos y síntomas resultantes de la obstrucción parcial o\\Ncompleta del flujo sanguíneo a través de la vena cava superior (VCS). (1)","guid":"5usjrEOneEXdWCs07vhMuQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"- Reseña histórica: Descrito por primera vez por William Hunter en 1757. (4)","guid":"4lnGZfimA4ONuJG7NAS7Eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"117","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- La VCS es responsable del drenaje venoso de la cabeza,\\Ncuello, extremidades superiores y tórax superior. (1)","guid":"FeWajz-mBH6VMO4o9Jrfuw","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"- La obstrucción de la VCS conduce a un aumento de la presión venosa,\\Ncausando edema y congestión en las áreas drenadas por la VCS. (1)","guid":"NP3kdNvDps1MUELJl1s-_g","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"- Objetivos terapéuticos: Aliviar la obstrucción, tratar la\\Ncausa subyacente y prevenir complicaciones. (3)","guid":"or_TC6VTnV1Sc4gvE1XVjA","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"- Investigación futura: Nuevas terapias dirigidas y técnicas de\\Nintervencionismo para el manejo del SVCS. (5)","guid":"Oe0EKbJi_8J9m9tChbk6sA","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"117","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"- Incidencia estimada: 15,000 casos por año en EE.UU. (6)","guid":"T2prUq6ydHtVKlGr2AnJsA","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"- Morbilidad: Edema facial, disnea, tos, dolor torácico, disfagia y cambios visuales. (1)","guid":"gHQFgaJ0N6k0PAG8y9Veog","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"- Letalidad: Depende de la causa subyacente, siendo el cáncer de pulmón la más letal. (1)","guid":"UrYbkOAcTuXv67A5ds8lkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"117","text":"Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"- Cáncer de pulmón (60-80%) (1)","guid":"em1yd882nqsjYlKQcDBMSg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"- Linfoma (10-15%) (1)","guid":"_so0PlZvaZvJzQ3ZPpQBMA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"- Metástasis mediastínicas (5-10%) (1)","guid":"G4w6LtaeCbQ3lR5TmClEyA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"- Causas benignas\\N(<5%) (1)","guid":"Z_gyFB-pT008ghTopW9X5A","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"- Fibrosis mediastínica","guid":"fV58sIvdtObsqsC3Ybjacw","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"- Infecciones (tuberculosis, histoplasmosis)","guid":"xJuqnpyTjad8351Si_NkgQ","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"- Trombosis venosa","guid":"D8jEw6Fgse78yu3-YQKYRQ","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"- Catéteres venosos centrales","guid":"DoHbd2K3phRlX-aR28URsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"134","text":"- Otras (<1%) (1)","guid":"O6OIFJOeu9SjUKz6lPaMAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"117","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"b0mFhF0_FlaGGDU2G2t89w","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"- Cáncer de pulmón (RR: 5.0) (7)","guid":"DpNtGLQjntH0OppCyzeMng","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"- Linfoma (RR: 2.5) (7)","guid":"t0aE0_d_rmSQxUePOkx-_g","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"- Uso de catéteres venosos centrales (RR: 1.8) (7)","guid":"DBNk9IEPnZEPfVUeK5Do_A","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"- Trombosis venosa (RR: 1.5) (7)","guid":"5xDLn_s3u8xiDfS_Pt5b6g","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"- Linfoma de\\NHodgkin (LH)","guid":"yocgm8q5ysJPp5goJxHvrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"117","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"- Antecedentes: Historia de cáncer, uso de catéteres\\Nvenosos centrales, trombosis venosa previa. (1)","guid":"OSlkUW8yNIRHIWNn1chiGA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"- Cuadro clínico (1,8):","guid":"xWH2Gz8bynNllS6j5BV79A","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"- Edema facial y en\\Ncuello (82%)","guid":"BdBhmvAQC3rsJQNzHVzA2g","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"- Disnea (54%)","guid":"afl4WaVWhqpAAAuzl9pthA","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"- Tos (45%)","guid":"LvXAHxPXpzbg1d9cIpEO4Q","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"- Dolor torácico (15%)","guid":"lNj7G-tb3__JdapkZA-Wpg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"- Disfagia (12%)","guid":"1_WIbuRJRIJqjyciOakIMQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"- Cambios visuales (2%)","guid":"1sFJEWQT6VzdtTwtTrYOzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"150","text":"- Signo de Pemberton:","guid":"hnrRPxIIz3hfM9QB8Jo3pg","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"plétora facial cuando un paciente eleva ambos brazos por\\Nencima de la cabeza durante más de un minuto","guid":"NYzVarN7tqxWTdM9WgGn2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"150","text":"- Factores de mal pronóstico: Cáncer de pulmón, edad\\Navanzada, obstrucción rápidamente progresiva. (1)","guid":"DqgHgzUqS-r5n6IjsUNknA","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"150","text":"- Complicaciones: Edema cerebral, síndrome de dificultad\\Nrespiratoria aguda (SDRA), trombosis venosa profunda (TVP). (1)","guid":"VyIYXby5GccGoaY-babatg","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"117","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"- Laboratorio: Hemograma, bioquímica, coagulación. (1)","guid":"7UZrVBhxALgPRNjUDVpSkg","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"- Imágenes (1,2):","guid":"7l2jS64YGFj4wpxexqQthg","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"- Radiografía de tórax: Ensanchamiento\\Nmediastínico (LR+: 3.2)","guid":"YgHLhX17qdAb6sJpH_ZgVQ","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"- Tomografía computarizada (TC) de tórax: Disminución del\\Ncalibre de la VCS (LR+: 7.5), masa mediastínica (LR+: 5.8)","guid":"8SQUXkwDHdQuFhC0nAwKEA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"- Resonancia magnética (RM): Útil para\\Nevaluar la extensión de la obstrucción","guid":"xl8CgS-YAo1LfDYO1ayejQ","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"- Biopsia: Guiada por TC o mediastinoscopia\\Npara confirmar etiología. (1)","guid":"VQpKFf_REf7gs1ZgOttL3Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"117","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"- Diagnóstico sindrómico: Basado en la clínica y estudios de imágenes. (1)","guid":"8ykI_keH9Rcg8kxS_7scNA","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"- Criterios diagnósticos: No existen criterios específicos,\\Nse basa en la clínica y hallazgos imagenológicos. (1)","guid":"RCnp_gW5uannoPlA-8isxQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"- Gold Standard: TC de tórax con contraste. (2)","guid":"LQF4z2oUxRswAUeFhX3BRw","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"- Sensibilidad y especificidad de la TC: 96% y 92%, respectivamente. (2)","guid":"_07Ek6qy63iXXDRW8RmWIw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"117","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"- Síndrome mediastínico: Linfoma, timoma,\\Nquiste broncogénico, teratoma. (1)","guid":"ZrImJ8cjzKTVnOYo-nJmsg","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"- Trombosis venosa profunda (TVP) (1)","guid":"VJAjklu6PZKojwgje7TudQ","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"- Insuficiencia cardíaca congestiva (ICC) (1)","guid":"gTcoYmKskdfZTuJ9sq2Xsg","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"- Pericarditis constrictiva (1)","guid":"exDj-6bQNjQVpcH5-KLEPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"117","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"- Objetivo: Aliviar la obstrucción y tratar la causa subyacente. (3)","guid":"uxnD_TnAL5T8Ef0pOaTFyw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"- No farmacológico: Elevación de la cabeza, oxigenoterapia. (3)","guid":"6yr3bE5Y7gG99X4g8Ug-lA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"- Farmacológico (3):","guid":"LBDHV7ocaTEOERNDqL0wVw","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"- Primera línea:","guid":"d55sostYvxHHMTRUXNGF1A","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"- Radioterapia (20-30 Gy en 5-10 fracciones) para cáncer de pulmón y linfoma.","guid":"-sj0W9Vv9U3t-C10A502zA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"- Quimioterapia según el tipo de cáncer.","guid":"iNnwLdrhi7697ElGQG04nQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"- Segunda línea: Stents endovasculares para obstrucciones refractarias.","guid":"czoCWVKn1pPDXPfxX4FVTA","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"183","text":"- Tercera línea: Anticoagulación para trombosis venosa.","guid":"2PJG_5ZCDQsFOisVnjv3kg","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"180","text":"- Efectos adversos: Esofagitis por radioterapia,\\Ntoxicidad por quimioterapia. (3)","guid":"QbAGnjwtAFtktBkYtpdkXw","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"180","text":"- Interacciones: Varían según los agentes\\Nquimioterapéuticos utilizados.","guid":"Gr6xRIAMt0OLrmmdmTONag","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"180","text":"- Farmacocinética y\\Nfarmacodinamia: Dependen de los\\Nagentes específicos utilizados.","guid":"GWW6kxHUIpPNDKAD5kPYuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"117","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"- Seguimiento: Clínico y con TC de tórax cada 3-6 meses,\\Nsegún la etiología y respuesta al tratamiento. (1)","guid":"7gjnmwDaeBWCTFSMT5cU3w","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"- Pronóstico: Depende de la causa subyacente,\\Nsiendo peor para cáncer de pulmón avanzado. (1)","guid":"bX3b_T_fdL_tCdI0y2uuKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"117","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"- Mayor riesgo de complicaciones por\\Ncomorbilidades y fragilidad. (11)","guid":"mwijvC7LD5ZrTnJQfLuefw","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"- Considerar el estado funcional y las preferencias del\\Npaciente al decidir el tratamiento. (11)","guid":"WxHLt36704AsEpP3mpIGVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"117","text":"Referencias:","guid":"uAG7MAc3OwkOOXFEqtdyEA","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"1. Wilson LD, et al. Superior vena cava\\Nsyndrome with malignant causes. N Engl J\\NMed. 2007;356(18):1862-9.","guid":"W7VysrVdG_R_y1uXyGW5FQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"2. Lepper PM, et al. Superior vena cava\\Nsyndrome in thoracic malignancies. Respir\\NCare. 2011;56(5):653-66.","guid":"2-XzJcAO9ok9AS18VAKnng","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"3. Straka C, et al. Review of evolving etiologies,\\Nimplications and treatment strategies for the superior vena\\Ncava syndrome. Springerplus. 2016;5:229.","guid":"OAtNn0uvsxkygyjS_yI6Aw","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"4. Hunter W. The history of an aneurysm of the\\Naorta, with some remarks on aneurysms in general.\\NMed Obs Inq. 1757;1:323-57.","guid":"kH0MWajj1XSDFydKCZEsuQ","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"5. Lanciego C, et al. Endovascular stenting as the\\Nfirst step in the overall management of malignant\\Nsuperior vena cava syndrome. AJR Am J\\NRoentgenol. 2005;184(2):533-7.","guid":"Gw8rfNsCsy3tVqSVodTagQ","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"198","text":"6. Wan JF, et al. Superior vena\\Ncava syndrome. Cardiol Rev.\\N2020;28(5):245-250.","guid":"50Ko0BXQehXA6IHZFtKOwA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"198","text":"7. Rice TW, et al. Superior vena cava syndrome in\\Nthe United States: Clinical features and outcomes\\Nfrom the National Inpatient Sample. J Thorac Dis.\\N2021;13(3):1701-1710.","guid":"lIqvtOV4MNfRyWdNs9MPeQ","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"198","text":"8. Yellin A, et al. Superior vena cava\\Nsyndrome. The myth--the facts. Am Rev\\NRespir Dis. 1990;141(5 Pt 1):1114-8.","guid":"0MvecHe_8sVnRXpgaIJUFg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"198","text":"9. Ettinger DS, et al. NCCN Guidelines Insights: Central\\NNervous System Cancers, Version 2.2021. J Natl Compr\\NCanc Netw. 2021;19(11):1181-1195.","guid":"Vv9NllA9xPO-b7e4ttj_Sg","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"198","text":"10. Cheng S. Superior vena cava syndrome: a\\Ncontemporary review of a historic disease.\\NCardiol Rev. 2009;17(1):16-23.","guid":"UVYuBlPTti6Y47xrh8a93g","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"198","text":"11. Co MLM, et al. Superior vena cava\\Nsyndrome in the elderly. Clin Geriatr\\NMed. 2021;37(1):155-164.","guid":"2lxIisgvxWyHNH8SF2cI-A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"93","text":"- Signos de\\Nmetástasis","guid":"MIdcyUlIr3N6pzRGpQC5VQ","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"- Adenopatías supraclaviculares","guid":"hjc8Ksd_fnndeQYv414xqA","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"- Hepatomegalia","guid":"-GGHiwahckf1B0afvvzouA","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"- Lesiones cutáneas","guid":"1uvWs1FwJI2vXq5Fct92YA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"40","text":"3. Estudios de\\Nlaboratorio (3)","guid":"fw79wKM2FLGcJ9eyGIdBUw","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"- Hemograma completo","guid":"lUP_FTzyrBQeiojev2xLzA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"- Perfil bioquímico","guid":"SlJnktvOyplLNirR5MKE5w","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"- Función renal","guid":"v-8912npa1k2bVsYeBIgFQ","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"- Función hepática","guid":"qJDgvv6gCYmbOhysJ19XwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"214","text":"- Marcadores\\Ntumorales (optativo)","guid":"7P1aOrInhhxKpoOKK3OzHg","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"- CEA","guid":"NRYykoqgMnudJVXax_pxfQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"- CYFRA 21-1","guid":"qe5JfU_zArDj6Pb3C9A7cQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"40","text":"4. Estudios de\\Nimágenes (4)","guid":"3uPjHpSLnA2hzF5WuCFHRA","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"- Radiografía de tórax (PA y lateral)","guid":"LATFd2Rb2_446n7Xqv1IUw","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"- Tomografía computarizada (TC)\\Nde tórax con contraste","guid":"_27CdYPo96-dbq0aAPFRFw","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"→ Evaluación de tumor primario,\\Nganglios linfáticos y metástasis","guid":"I_MzruU0TFap8C-vBZkHRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"- PET-TC (opcional)","guid":"YH0uShK09IrAtXaiQDuFfw","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"→ Detección de metástasis ocultas","guid":"Vpu9VwvxbA9jEAwbiDhHgg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"40","text":"5. Estudios de\\Nestadificación (5)","guid":"FfjkE76QqsTMkoP5dKhGuA","children":[{"id":"229","parent":"228","text":"- TC de abdomen superior","guid":"0sijmHDZi93g9E5kT5ETpQ","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"228","text":"- TC o RM de cerebro","guid":"NmArmxVx_Ert5pN-kcQLvA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"228","text":"- Gammagrafía ósea o PET-TC","guid":"Ny9Uix9BPNnamOTCtM-QhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"40","text":"6. Confirmación\\Nhistológica (6)","guid":"vlP0hYvT6SUtBvvI4H-QVA","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"- Fibrobroncoscopía con biopsia transbronquial","guid":"HoPfAd8nmCL_mYdNX_PvJw","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"- Biopsia por punción transtorácica guiada por TC","guid":"a5UZ7wvVRgNVDZGDqMt_yg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"232","text":"- Toracoscopía o toracotomía","guid":"Re_DY6Py8awTMRa27f7PLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"40","text":"7. Estudios de biomarcadores\\N(en adenocarcinoma) (7)","guid":"kZCyvkjydYqGOcnTdgvOaw","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"- Mutaciones de EGFR","guid":"4qpcXW91j9c-c02JaGfpAg","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"- Reordenamientos de ALK y ROS1","guid":"opFAW0S90AlJjdP3rXB5lw","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"236","text":"- Mutaciones de BRAF","guid":"WIhJvZAG3coczLNW7Sp2Ug","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"236","text":"- Expresión de PD-L1","guid":"l4NN7WNqaOk5nSKuO9Ngzw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"0","text":"8. Evaluación de la\\Nfunción pulmonar (8)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"- Espirometría","guid":"rrCIQWkH3ZkDCWd5D3CyQg","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"241","text":"- Difusión de monóxido de carbono (DLCO)","guid":"zbululJnX4IesjazwbDOuw","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"0","text":"9. Evaluación del\\Nestado funcional (9)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"ECOG/OMS","guid":"AEUoA-ezcd9TyIoZfxPq6w","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"Grado 0 (ECOG-0) → Totalmente activo, sin restricciones","guid":"QhTuocyaL3poZz4v_XwHNg","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"245","text":"Grado 1 (ECOG-1) → Restringido en actividades físicas extenuantes, ambulatorio y capaz de trabajos livianos","guid":"BBup4Rw5hlgEIkFgubefJw","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"245","text":"Grado 2 (ECOG-2) → Ambulatorio y capaz de cuidado personal, pero incapaz de trabajar. Hasta 50% de tiempo despierto en cama.","guid":"OSaV5FAsqMmcORFPbBSnSA","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"245","text":"Grado 3 (ECOG-3) → Capaz de limitado autocuidado, confinado a cama/sillón más de 50% de tiempo despierto.","guid":"iOHUMRLLDC4GQg7sX7zg3Q","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"245","text":"Grado 4 (ECOG-4) → Completamente discapacitado, no puede realizar autocuidado, totalmente confinado a cama/sillón.","guid":"JczGV5ZZ6_IsTVk3FIVDPw","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"245","text":"Grado 5 (ECOG-5) → Muerto","guid":"I05OCPt84qwh5Bh9XnIHPA","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"245","text":"Uso:","guid":"osUyy2NkLdl5xq4XUQJaFw","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"- Evaluar estado funcional del paciente","guid":"j2gb5YJgrAWCZZtzJ84GSg","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"252","text":"- Determinar pronóstico y tratamiento","guid":"Wt1DnQW0lKqo9F-LVAEOQQ","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"252","text":"- Medir toxicidad de tratamientos","guid":"U2RDRuzlYrQvbvNjkH1TXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"245","text":"Referencias:","guid":"Wznko5d2H4xqAH4GoG4mDg","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"- Oken, M.M., et al. (1982). Toxicity and response criteria of\\Nthe Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group. American Journal\\Nof Clinical Oncology, 5(6), 649-655. https://doi.org/10.\\N1097/00000421-198212000-00014","guid":"WXfJX39-Z9NSI--aUxb-gA","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"256","text":"- Buccheri, G., Ferrigno, D., & Tamburini, M. (1996). Karnofsky and\\NECOG performance status scoring in lung cancer: a prospective,\\Nlongitudinal study of 536 patients from a single institution. European\\NJournal of Cancer, 32A(7), 1135-1141. https://doi.org/10.\\N1016/0959-8049(95)00664-8","guid":"uY6DNIu73OwHMX04_7H5_g","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"256","text":"Nota: Esta representación esquemática está diseñada para facilitar\\Nel estudio y la comprensión de la Escala de Estado Funcional de la\\NECOG/OMS. Puedes copiar y pegar este texto directamente en la\\Naplicación SimpleMind Pro o en cualquier otra herramienta de\\Nmapas mentales.","guid":"KcTjKIm-xToR0OZStMwu3w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"244","text":"Índice de\\NKarnofsky","guid":"8NBLMFjkZ8fxk-XQ7_wcYA","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"Evalúa el estado funcional de pacientes con cáncer.","guid":"zhiO8-u28zr5-tCSoWZepA","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"260","text":"Desarrollado por Karnofsky & Burchenal, 1949.","guid":"d8nJXsJUyyacqhUqyDZVZg","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"260","text":"Puntuación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"100 → Normal, sin síntomas","guid":"c8V6ML4w1gtj1ERIc5sPBA","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"90 ↓","guid":"YCr9clzDdubQdHL2OCZL6g","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"80 ↓ Actividad normal con esfuerzo","guid":"vuik2rzyiyRh363LoyNRlQ","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"263","text":"70 ↓ Cuida de sí mismo, trabajo limitado","guid":"XLInAROFntfQIZX20WeHNQ","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"263","text":"60 ↓ Requiere asistencia ocasional","guid":"J6sFap3p1fXf3UqW66lyZQ","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"263","text":"50 ↓ Requiere asistencia considerable","guid":"3MIEZSqOc7MAH25TVdg6XQ","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"263","text":"40 ↓ Discapacitado, cuidados especiales","guid":"yAuOGwHz4An7Hp2xKhxiKA","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"263","text":"30 ↓ Severamente\\Ndiscapacitado,\\Nhospitalización","guid":"cSCJCaa1XzN8O5a9MubzCw","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"263","text":"20 ↓ Enfermedad muy avanzada,\\Ntratamiento de soporte","guid":"n_Q5-i4Qt4F7Xf1UN3uRWg","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"263","text":"10 ↓ Moribundo,\\Nproceso fatal","guid":"l0I0lm2XbnAuMl4MUqt_xg","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"263","text":"0 → Muerto","guid":"S8qJmbBwwI7LUq_sWxgGyg","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"260","text":"Uso:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"- Evaluar evolución del paciente","guid":"eKvu968TfWbfn9QeYdbwyg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"- Determinar pronóstico","guid":"yz8B_nolPXXJEAt6Mf8rcg","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"- Planificar tratamiento según estado funcional","guid":"8EM-otfRgMULlrtys3MqWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"279","parent":"260","text":"Referencias:","guid":"yPr_b7efMTbWigcPz2QyXQ","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"- Karnofsky, D. A., & Burchenal, J. H. (1949). The clinical\\Nevaluation of chemotherapeutic agents in cancer. En C. M.\\NMacLeod (Ed.), Evaluation of chemotherapeutic agents (pp.\\N191-205). Columbia University Press.","guid":"27UWDmWfYcRYXZa_KXFrFA","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"279","text":"- Buccheri, G., Ferrigno, D., & Tamburini, M. (1996). Karnofsky and\\NEC